node.text:
I’m still learning about this movement and how to get involved effectively. 
In my research I found this advice which I will be following. I hope you will also find this helpful.

blackouttuesday today. There is strength in numbers, it’s important to speak up and show your support. 
I want change. Don’t you?

If you don’t understand why Black Lives Matter exists then please read the stories of countless people like George Floyd, Willie Simmons and Breonna Taylor. 
Don’t just post a black image and move on with your life. Do SOMETHING. Sign petitions if you’re legally able to, write to your government and donate if you can.
